
While offensive security is focused on breaking into system (attacks) the deffensive security does the opposite. 
It prevents the attacks and helps to find "holes" in the system. It also detects the intrusions
The team of deffensive security is called BLUE TEAM
Some of their tasks include :

-user cyber security awareness
-documenting and managing assets
-updating, patching and fixing systems
-setting up preventative security devices
-setting up logging and monitoring devices

QA
What would you call a team of cyber security professionals that monitors a network and its systems for malicious events? ---security operation center
What does DFIR stand for? ---Digital Forensics and Incident Response
Which kind of malware requires the user to pay money to regain access to their files? ---ransomware
